data.description: Del Webb 55+ active adult community with amenity center, resort pool, tennis, pickle & bocce ball. Beautiful east facing Sonoma Cove plan with immaculate stone flower beds & golf cart garage on a cul de sac lot featuring large fenced backyard with views of walking trail & pond. This amazing home features nearly $70K in Builder Upgrades + $40,000 in Owner Upgrades. Gorgeous finishes throughout including Luxury vinyl plank wood-look floors and faux cedar beam. This bright & open floor plan features a spacious family room, private study, formal dining, & flex room. The flex room directly off the kitchen could serve as a guest room and offers a wet bar with built-in combo fridge-freezer, a cozy stone fireplace with cedar mantle and an abundance of cabinet space. Stunning open kitchen boasts stylish gold pulls, large island, breakfast bar, & beautiful white quartz counters. Oversized covered patio offers Magnatrac electric shades rated for 75 mph winds.
